overview: Sportscaster and Wyoming native Curt Gowdy narrates this hunting film that offers a unique and exciting view of marksmen, with their rifles and bows, pursuing 30 majestic whitetail bucks in five separate expeditions in the North American wilderness. A must for hunting and outdoors enthusiasts, King of the North also includes hunting tips, fascinating facts about whitetail deer, and a photo gallery.
title: King of the North
